      "id": "file:packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/empty.go",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "empty.go",
      "filePath": "packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/empty.go",
      "summary": "Empty 后端实现：在内存中按 block size 返回全零字节，含可写 header 元数据。 完全派生自内存，无 mmap/file 依赖；常用于注入 base 为零的基础镜像。",
      "tags": [
        "block-storage",
        "zero-backend",
        "header"
      ],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/fetch_session.go",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "fetch_session.go",
      "filePath": "packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/fetch_session.go",
      "summary": "fetchSession：同 chunk 并发读取的协调器，使用 cond var 在 advance/setDone 时唤醒所有 waiter。 支持 partial-progress 推进、fail 传播、context cancellation，并通过 cache 回查。",
      "tags": [
        "concurrency",
        "session",
        "block-storage",
        "cond-var"
      ],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/fetch_session_test.go",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "fetch_session_test.go",
      "filePath": "packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/fetch_session_test.go",
      "summary": "fetchSession 并发测试：覆盖快路径、渐进推进、setDone 唤醒所有、失败传播、context 取消。 并发场景通过 goroutine 与 sync.WaitGroup 注入竞争。",
      "tags": [
        "test",
        "session",
        "concurrency"
      ],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/iov.go",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "iov.go",
      "filePath": "packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/iov.go",
      "summary": "Linux IOV/drain 工具：探测系统 IOV_MAX 与对齐的 process_vm_readv 最大 iov 数量。 drainIovs 是泛型化工具，将结构体数组的字节向量逐块写入目标 fd，简化多区域复制。",
      "tags": [
        "utility",
        "syscall",
        "iov",
        "linux"
      ],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/local.go",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "local.go",
      "filePath": "packages/orchestrator/pkg/sandbox/block/local.go",
      "summary": "文件型后端 Local：将指定 rootfs 文件按 block size 暴露，提供 Header/Slice 等。 适用于本地 envd 镜像文件直接 slice 给 overlay 层。",
